SUBSTITUTE FOR
HOUSE BILL NO. 5936
A bill to amend 1994 PA 451, entitled
"Natural resources and environmental protection act,"
by amending section 1307 (MCL 324.1307), as amended by 2018 PA 631.
THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF MICHIGAN ENACT:
1 Sec. 1307. (1) By the processing deadline, the department
2 shall approve or deny an application for a permit.
3 (2) If requested by the permit applicant, the department shall
4 extend the processing period for a permit by not more than 120
5 days, as specified by the applicant. If requested by the permit
6 applicant, the department may extend the processing period beyond
7 the additional 120 days. However, a processing period shall must
8 not be extended under this subsection to a date later than 1 year
9 after the application period ends.
